      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NO FIZZY DRINK (4) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot before finishing third (23.06) and beaten 2.25 lengths over 400m at this track. Top prospect. NEON BLUE (1) did a good job to finish third last time out over 400m at this track (23.20) in a Grade 6, the second top-three finish on the trot. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. WEBLEC SNIP (8) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fifth wasn't far away finishing 4.5 lengths from the winner (23.20). Key runner who gets his chance to atone. LOVE SHINE (6) hit the frame here last time and looks a chance again.",
